Sithe Energies Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















sithe energies inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Utilities
Industry: Utilities
Sub-Industry: Power Generation
Sithe Energies, Inc. develops, constructs and operates electric generating fa- cilities in the United States and Canada. The Company produces electricity from its gas-fired cogeneration plants and, to a lesser extent, from hydroelectric plants. Sithe sells electricity from its operating plants to major electric utilities and sells thermal energy to governmental and industrial clients.




