Projects

        The Sithe Global team has over 300 years of collective experience in development,
construction, and operations of electric generation facilities.
Our projects total 3,000 megawatts - a total
	capital investment potential of nearly $5 billion and are diversified across energy sources (hydro, gas and coal)
	providing cost-effective electricity across three continents.








