Global Alumina Corp.


                  Global Alumina Corp. engages in the development of an alumina refinery. Its business is the development, construction and operation of an alumina refinery near Sangaredi in the Prefecture of Boke, a major bauxite mining region of the Republic of Guinea together with a bauxite mine, power plant, port, railway, road and other ancillary infrastructure. The company was founded on May 26, 2004 and is headquartered in New York, NY.                




